00:34:32.159 --> 00:34:36.159
Sense, where i can just start typing right away, teach me

00:34:36.159 --> 00:34:40.159
Some python, for example.

00:34:40.159 --> 00:34:43.159
And, you know, since this is interactive and web-based,

00:34:43.159 --> 00:34:47.159
There's some nice fortises that come with this in the sense of

00:34:47.159 --> 00:34:51.159
Like you get a little icon that you can click to copy to the

