You're maybe in a jupyter notebook, where it's convenient

00:35:43.159 --> 00:35:46.159
To have the streaming output displayed right there as you

00:35:46.159 --> 00:35:49.159
Submit input to the llm.

00:35:49.159 --> 00:35:53.159
So not only that, if the model responds with markdown syntax,

00:35:53.159 --> 00:35:57.159
Then you're also going to get some nice formatting and syntax

00:35:57.159 --> 00:36:02.159
Highlighting right there in the console as well.

00:36:02.159 --> 00:36:07.159
Similar to what we saw with databot, there is an ability to

00:36:07.159 --> 00:36:12.159
Export the chat conversation to a standalone html file.

