Some sentiment analysis.

00:39:56.159 --> 00:39:59.159
So i'm going to define, like, three different fields.

00:39:59.159 --> 00:40:03.159
A positive score, a negative score, and a neutral score.

00:40:03.159 --> 00:40:05.159
Define this sentiment class.

00:40:05.159 --> 00:40:08.159
And then use this slightly different method, chat

00:40:08.159 --> 00:40:13.159
Structured, of providing the sentiment class to kind of tell

00:40:13.159 --> 00:40:17.159
The llm this is kind of the actual data that i'm trying

00:40:17.159 --> 00:40:20.159
To extract from the input.

00:40:20.159 --> 00:40:24.159
And then here is an example of some text that i want

00:40:24.159 --> 00:40:27.159
To extract a sentiment score from.

00:40:27.159 --> 00:40:32.159
So i run that, and i get a positive, negative, and neutral

00:40:32.159 --> 00:40:35.159
Score on this text.

