Allows you to basically kind of program with the streaming

00:40:48.159 --> 00:40:51.159
Output as it comes in from the model.

00:40:51.159 --> 00:40:55.159
So this is just a real basic way to just kind of print out

00:40:55.159 --> 00:40:57.159
The input as they're coming in.

