Models are capable of and sort of what we've built around

00:42:11.159 --> 00:42:13.159
That.

00:42:13.159 --> 00:42:16.159
Certainly the models will try to write prose, and they're

00:42:16.159 --> 00:42:19.159
Getting pretty good at it, but it's not what we've designed

00:42:19.159 --> 00:42:21.159
Assistant for.

